    "MethodologyThis section outlines the methodology adopted in this study to integrate Llama 2 7b with the Google Query API, the dataset and training process employed, and the metrics used for evaluation.",
    "The approach is designed to enhance the model's accuracy and reduce instances of hallucination by leveraging real-time internet data.",
    "Integration ApproachThe integration of Llama 2 7b with the Google Query API was conceptualized through a modular architecture, enabling the model to query the API for real-time information as part of its text generation process.",
    "To formalize this integration, let us consider the function F representing the text generation process, where F: X × Y → Z.",
    "Here, X denotes the input text, Y represents real-time data fetched from the Google Query API, and Z is the output text.A custom interface was developed to facilitate seamless communication between the model and the API."
